<html>
<head>
	<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html">
	<meta charset="utf-8">
	
	<title>CycloneTCP Web Server Demo</title>
	
	<link rel="shortcut icon" type="image/x-icon" href="favicon.ico">
	
